"Vim configuration file, sep 2017
"Author; Anders Rochester
"-------------------------------------------------

"----------- mapping ----------------------------- 
nmap <C-C> :colorscheme zen<CR>
nmap <C-N> :set invnumber<CR>
nmap <CR> G
map rr :source ~/.vimrc
map b1 :set background=light

"----------- settings ---------------------------- 
set number nohlsearch showmode
set tabstop=4
set expandtab
set history=50 
